quoteText: Unless otherwise expressly provided herein, the invalidity or unenforceability of any provision of these Terms will not affect the validity or enforceability of any other provision, all of which will remain in full force and effect.
title: Invalidity of any portion of the Terms of Service does not entail invalidity of its remainder
